T1  - FROM INDIVIDUAL TO AGGREGATE LABOR SUPPLY: A QUANTITATIVE ANALYSIS BASED ON A HETEROGENEOUS AGENT MACROECONOMY*
AU  - Chang, Yongsung
AU  - Kim, Sun-Bin
Y1  - 2006/02/01
PY  - 2006
DA  - 2006/02/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1468-2354.2006.00370.x
